transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello? Nitin sir Namaskar.
Executive: Namaskar.
Customer: Kaise ho sir aap thik ho?
Executive: Boliye sir.
Customer: Sir Ujjwal baat kar raha tha India Mart se.
Executive: Haan boliye boliye.
Customer: Haan ji maine aapko mail share kiya tha parso dekha tha kya aapne?
Executive: Mujhe whatsapp pe bhejiye na sir ek baar.
Customer: Haan maine whatsapp mein bhi bheja hua hai aur aapko mail bhi kiya hua hai aur dono cheezon ka diya hua hai.
Executive: Haan haan kaun se mail se kiya na ek baar mujhe hi kariye main dekh ke aapko update karta hu. 
Customer: Maine mail pe Ujjwal Gupta ke mail se kiya aapko whatsapp message kiya lekin aap seen hi nahi kar rahe ho mera message.
Executive: Aap whatsapp pe ye ye wala number pe jispe call kar rahe hain na aap usko whatsapp message kijiye.
Customer: Bilkul aapke isi number pe hi maine aapko message kiya but aap number hi nahi number se maine message kiya lekin aap seen nahi kar rahe ho mera message.
Executive: Mujhe hi kijiye main dekhta hu kaun sa number hai. Ek minute dijiye aapka number ye hai na 9607422525 hai na?
Customer: Kya bole?
Customer: 96074
Executive: Haan.
Customer: 22525 yahi number hai na aapka? Aap bhej dijiye mujhe.
Executive: Haan bhej dijiye mujhe.
Customer: Dekhiye maine hello bheja abhi abhi aapko just.

Customer: Maine apna naam bhi aapko likh ke bheja hai abhi abhi whatsapp pe.
Executive: Thik hai thik hai proposal bhej diyega aapne usme?
Customer: Isme main aapko dono ka bhej raha hu thik hai jo better lage aap uska confirm kar dijiyega thik hai.
Executive: Thik hai. Bhej do bhej do.
Customer: Okay sir.
Executive: Thank you.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer says he sent email and WhatsApp message.

- Executive is not seeing the messages.



Resolution:

- Customer resent 'hello' on WhatsApp.

- Executive asked to send proposal on WhatsApp.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will send both proposals.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- email, whatsapp, proposal
